prodNameC: "西門子" N肌紅蛋白 乳膠試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.N Myoglobin Reagent: consists of lyophilized polystyrene particles coated with rabbit anti-human myoglobin antibodies; 3x2 mL.
2. N Myoglobin Standard: consists of lyophilized, pooled human sera supplemented with human myoglobin, 3x1 mL.
3. N Myoglobin Control: consists of lyophilized, pooled human sera supplemented with human myoglobin, 3x0.5 mL.
4. N Myoglobin Supplementary Reagent A: consists of a buffered rabbit serum solution; 3x0.5 mL.
5. N Myoglobin Supplementary Reagent B: consists of a detergent solution; 1x1.6 mL.
applicantName: 西門子醫療設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 臺北市南港區園區街3號2樓之2
efficacy: 透過乳膠顆粒增強技術，定量測定人類血清、肝素化或加入EDTA的血漿中肌紅蛋白。
